{
  "text": "First, GenAI's hallucination (Alkaissi & McFarlane, 2023), a phenomenon when the system generates texts that are semantically or syntactically plausible but are in fact incorrect or nonsensical, was found to be the most prevalent challenge of GenAI-assisted academic writing.",
